name: India Reynolds
description:
A request of @Bzas76. Sorry I couldn't work with an older dataset, mate, but I hope you'll like this one!

India Reynolds is a British model and social media celebrity, known for her recent stint in Love Island, among other things.

Update: Retrained from scratch, since my work process has changed quite a bit since I did this TI. I think the previous version, even if it was only a 200-step one, was very good, but perhaps slightly less accurate than desired. India looked gorgeous in almost every pic, though, which is why I was hesitant to update the model. I think this new version (2.0) captures her looks better without losing terrain in terms of beauty.

This new version is a 1000 step TI, trained on a dataset of 18 images.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (1nd1areyn0lds:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, long brown coat, turtleneck sweater, pale skin, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6".
